ActBudget Implementation Act, 2008
SubjectOrder Fixing October 20, 2010 as the Date of the Coming into Force of Certain Sections of the Act
PrecisOrder fixing October 20, 2010 as the day on which subsection 94(5) and sections 95 and 97-99 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2008, come into force, the consequence of which will be the dissolution of the CANADA MILLENIUM SCHOLARSHIP FOUNDATION and the repeal of all provisions of the Act relating to the Foundation.
